history.content:
Hello, do many eecs transfer students extend their curriculum to 5th semester?

Considering that they did not have credits for the lower-division requirements.

I know that it differs depending on the person but on average, how many units do transfer student take per semester?

How many technical courses per semester?

I'm trying to take upper division course next Summer without extending my curriculum to 5th semester (I believe Summer is not counted as regular academic semester), however, still my schedule will be really brutal taking 3 or 4 upper division courses for the following two semesters.
history.subject: Transfer student 5th semester
